# Type Safety Rules

1. **Export type hooks explicitly:**

```typescript
const player: RpgPlayerHooks = { ... }
const sprite: RpgSpriteHooks = { ... }
const client: RpgClientEngineHooks = { ... }
```

2. **Use type annotations on parameters:**

```typescript
async onAction(player: RpgPlayer) { }
onJoin(player: RpgPlayer) { }
```

